				<table width="100%" cellspacing="5">
				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Some sound drivers <em>do</em> reset back to the IPL just to load new audio data (or they support a command that can perform this). However, you'd need a comprehensive list of what command performs this particular action for the corresponding sound driver, and not all sound drivers actually do this (so, if possible, you'd probably have to use the sound driver's own load function to overwrite with code to reset back to IPL).</div>

					<br clear="all" /><br />

